                                                            <p style="color:rgb(53, 53, 53);"><br><span style="font-family:Roboto;"><span style="color:rgb(64, 64, 64);">26.1 Available methods of payments are determined by the country and the currency selected during registration. A complete list of fees, limits on them and other items is displayed on the Deposits and Withdrawals page. Alivecasino reserves the right to change these terms and details.</span></span><br>&nbsp;</p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgba(49, 49, 49, 0.7);"><span style="font-family:Roboto;"><span style="color:rgb(64, 64, 64);">26.2 When conducting any financial transactions it is necessary that the name of the owner of the debit/credit card or bank account exactly match the name of the owner of the appropriate account of Alivecasino . Otherwise Alivecasino reserves the right to cancel all transactions and make a return on all bets made while using someone else’s account or credit/debit card.</span></span></p>
